        "Javier De Las Rivas"
      ],
      "sc:description": "The ASURI (Analysis of SUrvival and patients RIsk prediction based on gene signatures) package discovers marker genes that are related to risk prediction capabilities and to a clinical variable of interest. It uses two main steps, including subsampling glmnet and unicox. The package implements robust functions to discover survival markers related to a clinical phenotype and to predict a risk score, allowing to study the patient's risk based on the gene signatures. Several plots are provided to visualise the relevance of the genes, the risk score, and patient stratification, as well as a robust version of the Kaplan-Meier curves.",
      "sc:license": "LGPL-3.0-only",
      "sc:name": "asuri",
      "sc:operatingSystem": [
        "Windows",
        "Linux",
        "Mac"
      ],
